{"tid":202442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"櫻花妹也比下去！台灣10所「夢幻女高中生制服」大盤點","createTime":"2017-04-15T13:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T04:52:17.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5c2881bf3882a213936304e18b89ae07e13261","tid":202442,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"青春無敵！在每個人的求學時代，多多少少都曾經穿上制服，只要在路上看見高中制服，有時就會想起當時的青春回憶，有些人更因為制服太好看，唔護子宮 即老10年！必學 護子宮調經2大動作而立志要考上學校，連寒暑假也要穿著，是一種榮譽的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n台灣各校的制服各有特色，但是有一些高中的搭配，更是大家都說讚，這次不比新資、城市發展，而是看潮流網站《JUSKY》所精選，10所網路上討論度爆高的「南北部高校女生制服」，其中水手服獲得許多人的喜愛，看來看看你喜歡的學校制服有沒有上榜吧。<br />\n<br />\n《北部代表》<br />\n1.北一女中<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459634.jpg&h=609b9683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.景美女中<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459635.jpg&h=ac31961d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.治平高中<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459636.jpg&h=22be91fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.穀保家商<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459641.jpg&h=4c1af52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.莊敬高職<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459646.jpg&h=46dffc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《南部代表》<br />\n<br />\n1.南英商工<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459680.jpg&h=668406a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.家齊女中<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459679.jpg&h=a672d25e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.高苑工商<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459677.jpg&h=b3f8c06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.樹德家商<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459676.jpg&h=7f52c0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.三民家商<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2459/d2459674.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2459%2Fd2459674.jpg&h=3d77c78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.嘉諾撒聖心學校私立部<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HmX704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HmX704.jpg&h=4c5c8954&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb3d8d7f0079735c192d214a9f461f2d7b4640ed","tid":202442,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"diu朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e800cf4b37b10ff28a2dca3ea1c822a89264e4b","tid":202442,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"根本係人嘅問題"},{"pid":"504a5bb9d658dcfc39e15cd3a03a1ae0b8df3fd2","tid":202442,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲女"},{"pid":"7d32d6eb0060f3a3f556255e292bac48e7e3b9ec","tid":202442,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係人嘅問題</blockquote><br />\n明明去台北旅行